cast.overview: Ja-yoon is a high school student who struggles with memory loss after she endured some unknown trauma during her childhood. While trying to uncover the truth, she is unwittingly dragged into a world of crime and finds herself on a journey that will awaken many secrets hidden deep within.
cast.title: The Witch: Part 1. The Subversion

details.biography:
Chung Ye Jin, previously known as Jung Woo Rim, is a South Korean actor under DSPmedia (디에스피미디어). She completed her studies at Dongduk Women's University's Department of Broadcasting and Entertainment.

Ye Jin made a significant career shift in 2018 when she joined JiKim Entertainment (지킴 엔터테인먼트와) under her real name.
details.name: Chung Ye-jin
